<i>It's been around for 100 years.</i>

276
00:39:23.820 --> 00:39:26.614
<i>but the family's roots
go back much further.</i>

277
00:39:27.949 --> 00:39:30.118
<i>Our founders discovered
a way to communicate</i>

278
00:39:30.201 --> 00:39:33.538
<i>with the other side
through a sacred conduit.</i>

279
00:39:35.206 --> 00:39:36.875
<i>They made a deal.</i>

280
00:39:36.958 --> 00:39:38.710
<i>Immortality.</i>

281
00:39:38.793 --> 00:39:41.379
<i>In exchange for human sacrifices.</i>

282
00:39:41.963 --> 00:39:44.465
<i>As long as your name is on the list.</i>

283
00:39:44.549 --> 00:39:46.050
<i>you cannot die.</i>

284
00:39:47.343 --> 00:39:49.679
<i>Most of the members are rich assholes</i>

285
00:39:49.762 --> 00:39:52.223
<i>with the power
to protect Virgil's secrets.</i>

286
00:39:52.348 --> 00:39:54.893
<i>They lure in poor bastards like you...</i>

287
00:39:54.976 --> 00:39:58.021
Virgil was built in 1923.

288
00:39:58.104 --> 00:40:00.064
<i>just to turn them into offerings.</i>

289
00:40:00.148 --> 00:40:01.816
<i>But once in a while.</i>

290
00:40:01.941 --> 00:40:05.820
<i>the chosen few are spared
and given the chance to join the family.</i>

291
00:40:05.945 --> 00:40:07.572
I'm so glad we didn't kill you.

292
00:40:07.697 --> 00:40:09.657
It is so hard to find good help.

293
00:40:10.241 --> 00:40:13.077
<i>Bust your ass.
and you might climb up the ladder.</i>

294
00:40:14.704 --> 00:40:15.788
<i>Like Lily.</i>

295
00:40:16.873 --> 00:40:17.874
<i>Fuck up.</i>

296
00:40:17.999 --> 00:40:20.835
<i>and your name
will be erased from the list.</i>

297
00:40:20.960 --> 00:40:22.837
<i>making you mortal again.</i>

298
00:40:23.713 --> 00:40:24.839
Fuck me!

299
00:40:24.964 --> 00:40:26.466
Aptly put.

300
00:40:26.549 --> 00:40:28.718
Because tonight. you are the offering.

301
00:40:30.094 --> 00:40:31.429
Wait. wait!

302
00:40:33.806 --> 00:40:36.087
I blew this bitch's head off.
and she still came after me.

303
00:40:36.142 --> 00:40:37.393
How do you kill them?

304
00:40:37.477 --> 00:40:39.687
Did you even listen to me?

305
00:40:39.771 --> 00:40:41.814
While they're on the list. you can't.

306
00:40:42.565 --> 00:40:45.526
You can only slow them down
for a few seconds. maybe a minute.

307
00:40:45.610 --> 00:40:46.778
depending on the damage.

308
00:40:46.861 --> 00:40:48.196
But I blew her fucking head off!

309
00:40:48.321 --> 00:40:49.781
She'll grow it back.

310
00:40:50.740 --> 00:40:52.158
They always come back.

311
00:41:21.854 --> 00:41:25.775
What if I chop them into
a thousand pieces and set them on fire?

312
00:41:25.900 --> 00:41:28.111
Even if there's one piece left.

313
00:41:29.112 --> 00:41:32.907
even a slice of skin
will still keep living on its own.

314
00:42:19.412 --> 00:42:21.122
What the hell is this place?

315
00:42:25.251 --> 00:42:26.419
Fuck floor.

316
00:42:27.545 --> 00:42:30.548
Immortality gets boring after a while.

317
00:42:30.673 --> 00:42:32.842
So each floor caters
to a different vice.

318
00:42:34.552 --> 00:42:36.429
If you're one of them.
why are you helping me?

319
00:42:39.015 --> 00:42:40.099
I have my reasons.

320
00:43:08.795 --> 00:43:09.921
Hold your fire.

321
00:43:10.046 --> 00:43:11.047
Let me out.

322
00:43:12.048 --> 00:43:13.758
Why did you lock me in here?

323
00:43:16.594 --> 00:43:17.637
Maria?

324
00:43:39.784 --> 00:43:40.910
I thought you were dead.

325
00:43:41.786 --> 00:43:43.037
I thought you were in prison.

326
00:43:45.456 --> 00:43:46.833
What are you doing here?

327
00:43:48.668 --> 00:43:50.378
I came here to save you. Butthead.

328
00:43:51.671 --> 00:43:54.215
This whole building. it's. like

329
00:43:54.924 --> 00:43:56.342
it's a satanic cult.

330
00:43:57.927 --> 00:43:59.679
They have human sacrifices.

331
00:44:02.265 --> 00:44:03.266
I know.

332
00:44:05.059 --> 00:44:06.102
You know?

333
00:44:07.979 --> 00:44:08.979
Yeah.

334
00:44:19.240 --> 00:44:20.825
Come on. Let's go.

335
00:44:48.019 --> 00:44:49.061
I don't get it.

336
00:44:49.145 --> 00:44:50.225
I found you on the streets.

337
00:44:50.313 --> 00:44:52.064
I give you shelter and a good job.

338
00:44:52.732 --> 00:44:54.442
Why would you tell the other girls I am.

339
00:44:54.567 --> 00:44:57.570
and I quote. "a fucking asshole"?

340
00:44:58.905 --> 00:45:01.324
I'm very grateful for everything
you've done for me. Richie.

341
00:45:01.449 --> 00:45:03.075
No. no. you're not.

342
00:45:03.159 --> 00:45:04.160
I am.

343
00:45:10.750 --> 00:45:13.127
Here's the thing. I want to believe you.

344
00:45:14.170 --> 00:45:15.922
But it's just words. y'know.

345
00:45:16.088 --> 00:45:17.288
And as we've just established.

346
00:45:17.340 --> 00:45:19.140
you can't really trust
what people are saying.

347
00:45:19.217 --> 00:45:24.722
Now. if you could do something
to prove you're grateful.

348
00:45:24.805 --> 00:45:27.475
well. maybe then I would believe you.

349
00:46:11.978 --> 00:46:15.523
It doesn't appear so.
but it's your lucky day.

350
00:46:17.441 --> 00:46:20.528
Ordinarily. we'd slit your throat
in the name of our Lord.

351
00:46:20.653 --> 00:46:25.241
but one of our maids
was just caught stealing.

352
00:46:26.117 --> 00:46:28.244
You could take her place.

353
00:46:28.369 --> 00:46:31.539
Finally stop struggling
and have a home where you belong.

354
00:46:32.456 --> 00:46:35.251
We'll take care of you. Understand?

355
00:46:38.087 --> 00:46:39.171
Splendid.

356
00:46:51.142 --> 00:46:52.560
This is my home now.

357
00:46:55.855 --> 00:46:58.441
I'm not going anywhere with you.

358
00:47:01.193 --> 00:47:03.863
Well. I'm not leaving without you.

359
00:47:05.031 --> 00:47:06.449
You already have.

360
00:47:10.328 --> 00:47:12.413
What? Do you think I need you?

361
00:47:14.206 --> 00:47:16.292
When I was a kid. I needed you.

362
00:47:18.044 --> 00:47:20.880
The night you abandoned me.
I needed you.

363
00:47:24.050 --> 00:47:25.134
While you were in prison

364
00:47:25.217 --> 00:47:29.055
and our piece-of-shit father was beating
the crap out of me. I really needed you.

365
00:47:31.057 --> 00:47:32.350
But you are too late now.

366
00:47:33.476 --> 00:47:34.602
I don't need you.

367
00:47:38.522 --> 00:47:39.523
Wow!

368
00:47:40.107 --> 00:47:41.108
Go ahead and run.

369
00:47:41.776 --> 00:47:43.235
Try not to get caught this time.

370
00:47:48.532 --> 00:47:51.952
Do you have any idea
what I went through to find you?

371
00:47:52.661 --> 00:47:53.746
I don't care.

372
00:47:54.538 --> 00:47:55.539
Fuck you.

373
00:47:55.664 --> 00:47:58.542
- No. Fuck you.
- No. bitch. Fuck you.

374
00:47:58.667 --> 00:47:59.919
Fuck you!

375
00:48:09.095 --> 00:48:10.971
Family reunions can be challenging.

376
00:48:11.764 --> 00:48:13.057
This changes nothing.

377
00:48:13.140 --> 00:48:15.101
She's coming with me
whether she wants to or not.

378
00:48:15.267 --> 00:48:17.770
You don't understand.
It's not that simple for her.

379
00:48:17.853 --> 00:48:18.853
I don't care.

380
00:48:20.564 --> 00:48:21.690
How do you get out of here?

381
00:48:22.691 --> 00:48:25.152
This whole building was designed
to be a death trap.

382
00:48:25.236 --> 00:48:28.447
All the windows are shatterproof.
You've seen the locks on the front door.

383
00:48:28.531 --> 00:48:31.158
Now. there is one way out.

384
00:48:31.242 --> 00:48:32.910
It's a fire escape ladder off the roof.

385
00:48:32.993 --> 00:48:34.995
But you have to go through
the ninth floor.

386
00:48:35.121 --> 00:48:36.721
and that's the last place
you want to be.

387
00:48:37.581 --> 00:48:39.166
Oh. hell. I'll help you.

388
00:48:39.959 --> 00:48:41.127
I'm done with this shit.

389
00:48:50.010 --> 00:48:52.596
You little son of a bitch!

390
00:48:58.978 --> 00:49:00.688
Hey! Have you seen her?

391
00:49:01.730 --> 00:49:02.731
Hey!

392
00:49:03.858 --> 00:49:05.025
Shit! Fuck!

393
00:49:05.109 --> 00:49:06.569
What happened to your head?

394
00:49:06.694 --> 00:49:10.823
What? I don't understand. You...

395
00:49:10.906 --> 00:49:12.324
What...

396
00:49:12.450 --> 00:49:13.868
Fuck floor!

397
00:49:14.869 --> 00:49:15.870
She's found her sister.

398
00:49:21.584 --> 00:49:22.585
You!

399
00:49:29.925 --> 00:49:30.926
Come on!

400
00:49:35.764 --> 00:49:36.891
Wait! Holy...

401
00:49:38.767 --> 00:49:39.768
Hey. get off!

402
00:49:54.450 --> 00:49:55.451
Fucking bitch!

403
00:49:56.368 --> 00:49:57.411
That is it.

404
00:49:57.495 --> 00:49:59.872
I'm done fucking around.
We need everyone.

405
00:49:59.955 --> 00:50:02.291
- Wait a minute.
- Not even a discussion.

406
00:50:02.374 --> 00:50:04.668
You fucking traitor.

407
00:50:04.793 --> 00:50:05.836
Go.

408
00:52:51.085 --> 00:52:53.379
Just tell me one thing.

409
00:52:54.254 --> 00:52:55.422
Why?

410
00:52:57.966 --> 00:53:00.135
I'm tired of paying the bill
with blood. Lily.

411
00:53:01.720 --> 00:53:03.722
Didn't bother you for 100 years.

412
00:53:05.891 --> 00:53:08.727
Back in the day.
when this neighborhood was a shithole...

413
00:53:10.771 --> 00:53:15.317
I convinced myself
that we were making things better

414
00:53:15.442 --> 00:53:17.695
by taking the scum off the streets.

415
00:53:19.321 --> 00:53:20.447
But now

416
00:53:22.783 --> 00:53:24.118
our victims are good people.

417
00:53:26.036 --> 00:53:27.788
There's nothing good about that girl.

418
00:53:27.871 --> 00:53:30.708
Oh. yeah? And what about
the previous one and the one before?

419
00:53:30.791 --> 00:53:32.334
There's nothing good about them. too?

420
00:53:34.628 --> 00:53:37.464
The world is not fair. Ray.

421
00:53:38.590 --> 00:53:40.175
I did not make it so.

422
00:53:41.301 --> 00:53:42.594
Shall I remind you

423
00:53:43.887 --> 00:53:47.933
what it was like for us
before we came to Virgil?

424
00:53:48.892 --> 00:53:50.060
I remember.

425
00:53:51.603 --> 00:53:52.730
We were all alone.

426
00:53:53.897 --> 00:53:55.482
We had each other.

427
00:53:56.233 --> 00:53:59.194
With the whole world against us.

428
00:54:00.487 --> 00:54:04.491
The family are the only ones
who accepted us.

429
00:54:05.325 --> 00:54:06.952
They gave us a home.

430
00:54:07.911 --> 00:54:09.538
This isn't a home. Lily.

431
00:54:11.039 --> 00:54:12.499
It's a fucking prison.

432
00:54:15.377 --> 00:54:16.795
Let's go make an announcement.

433
00:54:19.673 --> 00:54:23.677
If you still care for me. for us.

434
00:54:24.386 --> 00:54:27.848
I would think very seriously
about what you do next.

435
00:54:28.390 --> 00:54:31.226
This might be a prison.
but it's my prison.

436
00:54:37.232 --> 00:54:38.233
Watch him.

437
00:54:43.697 --> 00:54:44.782
You look better this way.

438
00:54:48.577 --> 00:54:51.914
<i>I apologize for the late announcement.</i>

439
00:54:51.997 --> 00:54:53.999
<i>I hoped it wouldn't come to this.</i>

440
00:54:54.082 --> 00:54:58.837
<i>but our offering is on the loose
in the building.</i>

441
00:54:59.713 --> 00:55:02.758
<i>Her real name is Asia Reaves.</i>

442
00:55:02.841 --> 00:55:05.844
<i>I just dropped her picture
in the group chat.</i>

443
00:55:05.969 --> 00:55:07.846
<i>We disabled the elevators.</i>

444
00:55:08.472 --> 00:55:13.393
<i>Every tenant. every floor.
be on the lookout.</i>

445
00:55:14.603 --> 00:55:16.855
<i>We need her alive.</i>

446
00:55:17.731 --> 00:55:20.108
<i>But feel free to make her suffer.</i>

447
00:55:20.984 --> 00:55:23.320
<i>Asia. mark my words.</i>

448
00:55:24.446 --> 00:55:28.450
<i>I will personally sacrifice you</i>

449
00:55:29.576 --> 00:55:30.744
<i>to our Lord.</i>

450
00:55:54.351 --> 00:55:55.936
Picked another fight you can't win.

451
00:56:01.358 --> 00:56:02.609
I can't watch you die.

452
00:56:04.444 --> 00:56:06.655
Get to the elevator shaft.
I'll try to distract them.

453
00:56:08.657 --> 00:56:09.825
You can still make it.

454
00:56:10.367 --> 00:56:11.368
Wait.

455
00:56:16.081 --> 00:56:18.208
Really wish things
had turned out differently.

456
00:56:42.399 --> 00:56:43.400
Maria!

457
00:58:35.804 --> 00:58:36.805
Run!

458
00:58:39.558 --> 00:58:41.518
You fuckers!

459
00:58:58.410 --> 00:58:59.411
Maria!

460
01:00:06.645 --> 01:00:08.605
How many of you are there?

461
01:00:43.140 --> 01:00:44.141
Give up!

462
01:01:30.145 --> 01:01:32.314
No. no! Wait! Wait!

463
01:01:34.566 --> 01:01:37.819
Listen. I know you think
we're terrible people.

464
01:01:37.903 --> 01:01:40.947
But if you get to know us better.
we're actually really nice.

465
01:01:41.031 --> 01:01:42.365
We spared your sister.

466
01:01:42.449 --> 01:01:44.409
Look. this is my wife. Anne.

467
01:01:44.492 --> 01:01:45.869
She liked you.

468
01:01:45.994 --> 01:01:47.037
You remember her?

469
01:01:51.416 --> 01:01:52.459
Maria?

470
01:02:07.432 --> 01:02:08.600
I missed you.

471
01:02:10.602 --> 01:02:11.770
I'm so sorry.

472
01:02:13.188 --> 01:02:15.649
I'm really sorry. I fucked up so badly.

473
01:02:15.774 --> 01:02:18.401
- I just... I...
- It's okay. It's okay.

474
01:02:18.485 --> 01:02:20.111
- I'm sorry.
- It's okay.

475
01:02:27.118 --> 01:02:28.662
You should have left me.

476
01:02:30.372 --> 01:02:31.456
Never.

477
01:02:39.381 --> 01:02:40.632
We have to get out of here.

478
01:03:04.864 --> 01:03:06.908
We checked upstairs. All clear.

479
01:03:06.992 --> 01:03:09.077
There's no way
she could have gotten past.

480
01:03:09.160 --> 01:03:10.160
Come on.

481
01:03:19.129 --> 01:03:20.171
Go!

482
01:03:22.674 --> 01:03:25.427
I'm sorry. Lily. We tried our best.

483
01:03:27.262 --> 01:03:29.180
Search the floor.

484
01:03:31.391 --> 01:03:32.391
Fuck.

485
01:03:33.310 --> 01:03:34.602
Let me see.

486
01:03:34.728 --> 01:03:35.729
It's fine.

487
01:03:35.854 --> 01:03:36.980
Let me see.

488
01:03:38.106 --> 01:03:39.107
Sit down.

489
01:03:46.489 --> 01:03:48.169
Where did you learn
how to fight like that?

490
01:03:52.787 --> 01:03:53.788
Prison.

491
01:03:55.332 --> 01:03:56.458
Was it tough?

492
01:03:57.584 --> 01:03:58.752
Better than living with Dad.

493
01:04:04.049 --> 01:04:05.425
You know he died two years ago?

494
01:04:06.468 --> 01:04:07.677
No shit.

495
01:04:07.761 --> 01:04:08.803
No shit.

496
01:04:09.929 --> 01:04:11.014
Did you kill him?

497
01:04:12.349 --> 01:04:13.350
No.

498
01:04:14.642 --> 01:04:15.643
Cancer.

499
01:04:19.189 --> 01:04:21.066
Look. I shouldn't have abandoned you
back then.

500
01:04:21.816 --> 01:04:24.361
You needed me to protect you from Dad.
and I wasn't there.

501
01:04:25.653 --> 01:04:28.533
I swear there isn't a day in the last
ten years that I don't regret that.

502
01:04:30.492 --> 01:04:31.910
You can't fix the past.

503
01:04:33.078 --> 01:04:34.120
No.

504
01:04:35.121 --> 01:04:37.665
But I thought. if we don't
make it out of here tonight.

505
01:04:37.749 --> 01:04:38.958
I wanted you to know that.

506
01:04:41.336 --> 01:04:43.046
Send more people to guard the entrance.

507
01:05:12.867 --> 01:05:14.536
- You good?
- Yeah.

508
01:05:37.392 --> 01:05:39.060
- Asia.
- Yes.

509
01:05:39.144 --> 01:05:40.854
Come on! Shoot him!

510
01:06:05.211 --> 01:06:06.212
Go!

511
01:06:13.595 --> 01:06:15.472
Oh. my God! Oh. my God!

512
01:06:26.774 --> 01:06:27.817
Fuck!

513
01:06:32.363 --> 01:06:33.364
That's it.

514
01:06:34.741 --> 01:06:35.783
It's over.

515
01:06:45.793 --> 01:06:46.836
No. it's not.

516
01:06:46.920 --> 01:06:48.213
You're ridiculous.

517
01:06:51.925 --> 01:06:53.801
You need me alive for the sacrifice.
don't you?

518
01:06:54.969 --> 01:06:56.137
Let Maria go.

519
01:06:56.221 --> 01:06:57.514
or I'll jump.

520
01:06:58.681 --> 01:07:01.226
- You can scrape up what's left.
- Asia. no.

521
01:07:01.392 --> 01:07:02.644
So selfless.

522
01:07:03.520 --> 01:07:05.063
And so misguided.

523
01:07:06.397 --> 01:07:08.399
Do you even know whose life
you're fighting for?

524
01:07:09.234 --> 01:07:10.234
Lily. please.

525
01:07:10.276 --> 01:07:12.403
The fuck are you talking about?

526
01:07:13.571 --> 01:07:14.822
Didn't you ever think...

527
01:07:15.990 --> 01:07:18.785
How exactly did your dear sister

528
01:07:18.868 --> 01:07:22.121
come from being
just another one of our sacrifices

529
01:07:22.247 --> 01:07:25.792
to have a chance to join our family?

530
01:07:26.417 --> 01:07:29.546
What deal has she made?

531
01:07:36.135 --> 01:07:37.845
We'll take care of you.

532
01:07:38.471 --> 01:07:39.847
Do you understand?

533
01:07:40.974 --> 01:07:42.100
Yes.

534
01:07:42.183 --> 01:07:43.309
Splendid.

535
01:07:44.310 --> 01:07:46.688
You will pledge to our Lord.

536
01:07:46.771 --> 01:07:51.192
When the time comes.
you will put your name on the list.

537
01:07:51.734 --> 01:07:54.571
Then you seal the deal with blood.

538
01:07:55.488 --> 01:07:57.156
You kill your sacrifice. dear.

539
01:07:58.783 --> 01:08:01.035
One death for one life.

540
01:08:01.160 --> 01:08:03.913
A small price for immortality.

541
01:08:05.039 --> 01:08:10.295
But if you break your word. run away.
or don't find an offering

542
01:08:12.338 --> 01:08:14.132
our Lord will take you.

543
01:08:18.761 --> 01:08:20.179
<i>I didn't want to hurt anyone.</i>

544
01:08:22.015 --> 01:08:23.600
<i>But there was no way out of this deal.</i>

545
01:08:25.101 --> 01:08:26.894
<i>I committed my soul to the Devil.</i>

546
01:08:28.896 --> 01:08:30.565
<i>Isabelle Davison.</i>

547
01:08:30.648 --> 01:08:33.776
<i>a woman from my last job.
was supposed to be my sacrifice.</i>

548
01:08:35.820 --> 01:08:36.821
It's a small tradition.

549
01:08:36.904 --> 01:08:38.781
<i>But instead. you showed up.</i>

550
01:08:38.906 --> 01:08:42.076
One of our maids will be
rewarded tonight for her dedication.

551
01:08:42.201 --> 01:08:43.953
<i>And now. I'm out of time.</i>

552
01:08:46.456 --> 01:08:48.041
To Isabelle's memory.

553
01:08:48.124 --> 01:08:49.459
To Isabelle.

554
01:08:49.542 --> 01:08:51.377
<i>- Salud.
- Salud.</i>

555
01:08:51.461 --> 01:08:53.129
<i>Without a sacrifice tonight...</i>

556
01:08:56.132 --> 01:08:57.258
<i>I'm dead.</i>

557
01:09:08.227 --> 01:09:10.313
I feel sorry for you. Asia.

558
01:09:10.396 --> 01:09:11.522
Honestly.

559
01:09:12.231 --> 01:09:15.360
All this for nothing.

560
01:09:15.443 --> 01:09:16.527
Take them.

561
01:09:17.528 --> 01:09:19.030
- No. No. no. no.
- Come on. Move!

562
01:09:19.113 --> 01:09:21.532
No! No! No!

563
01:10:05.743 --> 01:10:07.995
Now we go see the head.

564
01:10:13.584 --> 01:10:16.129
If he asks. just play along.

565
01:10:17.046 --> 01:10:18.506
I hope he's in a good mood.

566
01:11:25.698 --> 01:11:26.949
Pig on a stick?

567
01:11:27.784 --> 01:11:28.826
Really?

568
01:11:29.952 --> 01:11:32.246
Show some goddamn respect.

569
01:12:55.913 --> 01:13:00.251
The unclean spirit entered the swine.

570
01:13:01.252 --> 01:13:05.298
- My Lord we have a new offering for you.
- Fuck me.

571
01:13:05.381 --> 01:13:08.050
We also brought you Ray and Maria.
my Lord.

572
01:13:08.801 --> 01:13:10.553
They both have betrayed us.

573
01:13:16.100 --> 01:13:18.102
It was a lapse in judgment. m'Lord.

574
01:13:18.936 --> 01:13:20.521
Ray felt sorry for the girl.

575
01:13:22.148 --> 01:13:24.066
Liar.

576
01:13:26.569 --> 01:13:29.697
Ray is out.

577
01:13:42.668 --> 01:13:44.670
Kill him. Lily.

578
01:13:45.713 --> 01:13:47.131
Or die.

579
01:13:48.007 --> 01:13:50.384
No. please. I beg of you.

580
01:14:04.148 --> 01:14:05.858
No. no. No.

581
01:14:18.037 --> 01:14:19.580
I can't let you go.

582
01:14:21.040 --> 01:14:22.333
I made my choice.

583
01:14:24.877 --> 01:14:26.462
Now it's your turn. darling.

584
01:14:49.485 --> 01:14:50.528
Now. girls.

585
01:14:54.782 --> 01:14:56.200
Maria

586
01:14:57.118 --> 01:14:59.328
your time has come.

587
01:15:00.329 --> 01:15:02.331
I'm sorry. m'Lord.
I shouldn't have helped her.

588
01:15:03.082 --> 01:15:04.542
Please give me another chance.

589
01:15:05.793 --> 01:15:06.919
I'll do whatever it takes.

590
01:15:07.628 --> 01:15:08.629
What?

591
01:15:15.803 --> 01:15:19.515
Then kill your sister.

592
01:15:20.349 --> 01:15:21.350
Maria.

593
01:15:22.059 --> 01:15:23.060
Please.

594
01:15:25.271 --> 01:15:26.272
I'm sorry.

595
01:15:31.819 --> 01:15:33.821
Write your name.

596
01:15:34.947 --> 01:15:36.532
Join us.

597
01:15:36.657 --> 01:15:37.992
Thank you. m'Lord.

598
01:16:00.139 --> 01:16:01.182
Now

599
01:16:01.807 --> 01:16:04.143
seal the deal.

600
01:16:09.732 --> 01:16:11.108
I wish we had more time.

601
01:16:16.155 --> 01:16:17.865
This is the only way.

602
01:16:57.780 --> 01:17:01.200
I'm so sorry.

603
01:17:20.094 --> 01:17:21.095
Is she dead?

604
01:17:25.391 --> 01:17:26.559
Looks pretty dead to me.

605
01:17:44.660 --> 01:17:48.080
One death for one life.

606
01:18:10.019 --> 01:18:13.480
Maria sacrificed herself
to make Asia immortal!

607
01:18:14.315 --> 01:18:15.900
Holy fuck.

608
01:18:24.158 --> 01:18:26.452
Get the skin! Erase her name!

609
01:18:35.878 --> 01:18:36.921
Dude.

610
01:19:54.790 --> 01:19:56.000
Help me. my Lord.

611
01:20:53.766 --> 01:20:56.518
You want to play with swords?

612
01:20:56.643 --> 01:20:58.062
Let's play.

613
01:22:08.006 --> 01:22:09.383
Hey. Butthead.

614
01:22:09.842 --> 01:22:11.385
you should have left me.

615
01:22:12.010 --> 01:22:13.720
I'd still be alive.

616
01:22:14.888 --> 01:22:17.015
I died because of you.

617
01:22:19.393 --> 01:22:20.436
Leave

618
01:22:21.728 --> 01:22:23.605
my sister

619
01:22:25.315 --> 01:22:26.316
alone.

620
01:23:17.326 --> 01:23:19.369
I want my sister back.

621
01:23:19.828 --> 01:23:21.663
Of course you do.

622
01:23:21.788 --> 01:23:23.457
You know the deal.

623
01:23:23.540 --> 01:23:25.918
One death for one life.

624
01:23:28.253 --> 01:23:30.380
I think we can do better than that.

625
01:23:44.228 --> 01:23:45.229
Shit.

626
01:23:56.782 --> 01:23:58.450
Just a flesh wound.

627
01:24:12.422 --> 01:24:13.590
Oh. no.

628
01:24:28.146 --> 01:24:30.315
I'll see you

629
01:24:30.899 --> 01:24:32.693
in hell...

630
01:24:34.027 --> 01:24:35.904
Asia Reaves.

631
01:24:38.699 --> 01:24:40.576
I fucking hope so. bitch.

632
01:25:22.784 --> 01:25:25.787
If I were you. I'd clear out.

633
01:26:18.256 --> 01:26:19.424
What happened in there?

634
01:26:20.425 --> 01:26:21.426
Rich people.

635
01:26:38.026 --> 01:26:40.028
I'm... I'm...

636
01:26:40.153 --> 01:26:43.281
I'm just so sorry for your loss.

637
01:26:44.700 --> 01:26:46.159
I could take you wherever you...

638
01:26:47.619 --> 01:26:48.704
What is that?

639
01:26:53.417 --> 01:26:54.918
What the fuck is that?

640
01:26:55.585 --> 01:26:56.878
Jesus Christ!

641
01:27:03.176 --> 01:27:04.177
Maria.

642
01:27:05.762 --> 01:27:07.055
- Asia.
- What the fuck?

643
01:27:10.767 --> 01:27:11.768
What happened?

644
01:27:12.352 --> 01:27:15.772
Well. that's a great question.
because you were just fuckin' dead!

645
01:27:18.900 --> 01:27:20.360
<i>I changed my name to yours.</i>

646
01:27:21.194 --> 01:27:22.904
<i>And I killed all those motherfuckers.</i>

647
01:27:25.365 --> 01:27:27.784
What the hell are you two talking about?

648
01:27:32.664 --> 01:27:33.665
I told you.

649
01:27:34.374 --> 01:27:36.084
I'm never gonna leave you again.

650
01:27:50.807 --> 01:27:51.808
You know what?

651
01:27:52.642 --> 01:27:53.643
I don't want to know.

652
01:27:54.227 --> 01:27:55.395
Fuck it.

653
01:27:56.229 --> 01:27:57.397
Fuck it!

654
01:28:03.820 --> 01:28:04.821
Where we going?

655
01:28:05.530 --> 01:28:07.115
As far away from here as possible.

656
01:28:08.533 --> 01:28:10.368
I actually wouldn't mind some breakfast.

